    "TraditionalChinese": "食用產品"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "A refined food product, created in the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Nutrient Processor</span>. Food such as this can be <span class=\"name name-stellar\">highly valuable</span>. It has both the identifying shapes and aromas of an actual food item, in stark contrast with conventional nutrition paste or pellets.<br><br>Can be consumed as it stands or subjected to further processing.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "通过<span class=\"name name-technology\">营养处理器</span>制作的精制食品。这类食物的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">价值可以很高</span>，形状和气味上与真实的食品极为相似，和传统的营养剂或胶囊截然不同。<br><br>可直接食用或进一步加工。",
    "TencentChinese": "通过<span class=\"name name-technology\">营养处理器</span>生成的精制食品。<br><br>可直接食用或进一步加工。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">營養處理器</span>生成的精製食品。這種食物可能<span class=\"name name-stellar\">極為有價值。</span>它具有真正食物的外形和味道，和一般的營養糊或營養丸截然不同。<br><br>可直接食用或進一步加工。"
  },
